genresAdvancedInfo.name: nz jazz
genresAdvancedInfo.description: NZ jazz is a vibrant and innovative genre that showcases the talents of local musicians. It draws on a rich history of jazz music, incorporating elements of swing, bebop, and fusion. NZ jazz artists are known for their technical skill and improvisational prowess, and the scene has produced many world-class performers. The genre continues to evolve, with contemporary artists pushing the boundaries and exploring new sounds and styles.
